uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.iongen.model

Interface PeptideIon

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PrecursorIon, ProductIon
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPrecursorIon, AbstractProductIon, DefaultPeptideIon, DefaultPrecursorIon, DefaultProductIon

    public interface PeptideIon
    When a peptide with charges, we call it peptide ion. PrecursorIon and ProductIon are all belong to peptide ions. In the uk.ac.ebi.pride.iongen.model.impl.DefaultPeptideIon class, we provide the default implement, which pay main attention on mass and m/z calculate.
    Version:
    0.1-SNAPSHOT
    Author:
    Qingwei XU
